    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr)); gap:1rem;">
      <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border-left:2px solid #4CAF50; padding-left:0.8rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:white;">Faculty Authority</strong><br>Curriculum changes go through existing teacher and faculty governance structures. The ACIL coordinates — faculty approve.</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border-left:2px solid #4CAF50; padding-left:0.8rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:white;">Parent Consultation</strong><br>Families are consulted before adoption, not informed after. Pre-adoption listening sessions are required before any required course launch.</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border-left:2px solid #4CAF50; padding-left:0.8rem; line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:white;">Course Changes</strong><br>Course dissolution or new requirements go through board approval. AI audits identify; they do not eliminate.</div>
