    <div class="action-body">
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li><div class="check-box"></div><div class="check-content"><strong>AI Curriculum Integration Lead: Named, active, and compensated</strong><div class="check-why">Y/N and compensation amount. If N, this is the first failure point — everything else depends on it.</div></div></li>
